A BILL ENTITLED
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Forged Digital Likenesses – Distribution – Prohibition
3 FOR the purpose of providing that the distribution of a certain forged digital likeness to
4 another constitutes a statement or communication for the purpose of an action for
5 defamation; prohibiting a person from knowingly distributing a certain forged digital
6 likeness under certain circumstances; and generally relating to forged digital
7 likenesses.
